    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed per MRL 2 scope. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied across all five operating points with adequate uncertainty margins. The credibility assessment is accepted and the model is approved for regulatory submission support.",
